title: #92Noon! Wobby/Courtney Cronin/Birk/Coach Barone
description: PA, Nordo and Wobby talk never winning at Fantasy Football, and which knowledge is key. ESPN's Courtney Cronin schools us with her in depth observations of the upcoming season. Matt Birk and company (his kids), stop by. Vikings OL Coach Barone and Running Back Roc Thomas give their take.
